snippet.title: Frogs - (1978) - Arcade - gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Gremlin Industries © 1978
[Coin-Op] Arcade Video Game

Emulator: MAME 0.219


Now here's something a little different.  At least the action is smooth and purely arcade twitch.  Still a timed game, but they offer a FREE game if you just catch the dragonfly at the end.  I definitely had some fun with this, being simple enough to learn and enough randomness to make it a challenge for a good score.  I finally ended up with a best score of 6300.
